# SDX AI Readiness Testing - Project Rules

## Project Context

This is an AI testing tool project to evaluate how well AI coding assistants understand and apply the SDX (Swisscom Design System). We analyze Figma designs, compare with real code, and test AI-generated implementations.

## Critical Findings

**3 token systems co-exist** in SDX Figma without clear documentation:
1. Primary: `spacing/3`, `fontSize/heading/M` (most common)
2. SDX-Prefixed: `sdx/font/size/h2` (alternative)
3. Legacy: `space_old/baseline/2` (deprecated)

**Impact**: 60-95% AI failure rate on token consistency predicted.

